lvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-5850-fails-javac-compile-org.aesh-readline-3.0-3d966204\\n\\nThe original failure was in `:compileTestJava`: `TerminalBuilderTest.java` and `SignalsTest.java` referenced non-existent packages/symbols (`package org.aesh.readline.terminal does not exist`, `package org.aesh.readline.terminal.utils does not exist`, plus follow-on `cannot find symbol` errors for `TerminalBuilder` and `Signals`). See `human-intervention-logs/org.aesh:readline:3.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-04T22-31-29-436862Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/org.aesh:readline:3.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-04T22-32-23-516744Z.log`.\\n\\nThe preserved branch appears to contain a working fix for that compile problem: later local CI reruns passed `checkMetadataFiles`, `run-consecutive-tests`, and `checkstyle` in `forge/logs/check-metadata-files/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-04T23-23-14-368111Z.log`, `forge/logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-04T23-23-22-637842Z.log`, `forge/logs/check-metadata-files/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-04T23-24-23-319643Z.log`, `forge/logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-04T23-24-24-782846Z.log`, and `forge/logs/checkstyle/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-04T23-25-12-362558Z.log`.\\n\\nThe most likely remaining failing stage is metadata generation / agent-based verification, not the final local CI suite. Multiple `generateMetadata` attempts failed with `Could not find agent library native-image-agent on the library path, with error: libnative-image-agent.so: cannot open shared object file`, followed by `Execution failed for task ':test'` / `:generateMetadata`. See `human-intervention-logs/org.aesh:readline:3.0/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-04T23-09-03-420911Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/org.aesh:readline:3.0/metadata-fix/codex.log`. Metrics were still written successfully in `stats/org.aesh/readline/3.0/execution-metrics.json`, which suggests the code/test ch